t galaxies seems not much different from that\nin the nearby interstellar clouds. It presumably comprises, like for TMC-1,\naromatic rings and complex organic molecules putative precursors of the RNA\nnucleobases, except the lines of such species are too weak to be detected that\nfar.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 16 Jan 2022 18:18:26 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-01-19"}
