 estimated. We demonstrate the empirical\nperformance of the proposed method using simulation studies and a real\napplication to an eICU dataset as the source sample and a MIMIC-III dataset as\nthe target sample.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 17 Jan 2022 06:11:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 26 Feb 2023 04:35:17 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-02-28"}
